description	"A9 Republic Sentinel-Series War Droid MKI

(Based on a Super Battle Droid)

^2Weaponry:
- Disruptor Rifle (2)
-- Based on Bowcaster
-- 40% Slower Rate of Fire
-- Ignites Targets on Hit
-- Disintergrates targets on Death

^8Attributes:
- No Locational Damage
- Shield Regeneration (1)
- Magnetic Plating

^3Abilities:
- Recharge (1) ^3[CS1]
- Droid Flamethrower ^3[CS3]

A War Droid in use by Vaklu's forces. It is well armored and also comes with a close range flamethrower."